Installation
------------

suite_py is distributed on `PyPI <https://pypi.org>`_ as a universal
wheel and is available on Linux/macOS and Windows and supports
Python 2.7/3.5+ and PyPy.

.. code-block:: bash

    $ pip install suite_py
